  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nThere is a memory leak in the app resulting in huge memory consumption.\r\n\r\n![Screenshot from 2023-07-03 10-05-00](https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/33099791/ae8c0991-270a-41d9-8cba-2502d6b47cec)\r\n\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\nNot known, it is rather random. I faced it few times already, in most cases the app run for few hours. Additional factor may be recovery from OS sleep, although this I am unsure.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nRAM usage at max less than 1.5GB\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nRAM usage >6GB\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: 0.13.0 RC2\r\n- Operating System: Fedora 38\r\n\r\n",
